figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"KBWeyVMK0l\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/03/03/wp-env-simple-local-environments-for-wordpress/\">wp-env: Simple Local Environments for WordPress.</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;wp-env: Simple Local Environments for WordPress.&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/03/03/wp-env-simple-local-environments-for-wordpress/embed/#?secret=KBWeyVMK0l\" data-secret=\"KBWeyVMK0l\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Modification sur le traitement des requ√™tes d&rsquo;affichage de favicons</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"r61Qy7GJml\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/02/19/enhancements-to-favicon-handling-in-wordpress-5-4/\">Enhancements to favicon handling in WordPress 5.4</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Enhancements to favicon handling in WordPress 5.4&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/02/19/enhancements-to-favicon-handling-in-wordpress-5-4/embed/#?secret=r61Qy7GJml\" data-secret=\"r61Qy7GJml\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Et pour finir, un petit floril√®ge de modifications diverses et vari√©es</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Un article regroupe √©galement des modifications importantes vari√©es, dont  notamment&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Une meilleure information sur les erreurs au niveau de¬†<code style=\"font-size: 16px\">wp_login_failed</code></li><li>L&rsquo;ajout de l&rsquo;ID du site dans le filtre multisite¬†<code style=\"font-size: 16px\">newblog_notify_siteadmin</code></li><li>Un nouvel embed vid√©o pour TikTok</li><li>La suppression de l&#8217;embed CollegeHumor</li><li>Le stockage de l&rsquo;URL d&rsquo;origine des m√©dias attach√©s dans la m√©ta¬†<code style=\"font-size: 16px\">_source_url</code>¬†</li><li>Le chargement de la barre d&rsquo;administration en utilisant¬†<code style=\"font-size: 16px\">wp_body_open</code></li><li>La suppression des ID dupliqu√©s dans le widget Derniers commentaires</li><li>Un nouveau param√®tre dans l&rsquo;action <code style=\"font-size: 16px\">lostpassword_post</code>¬†de¬†<code style=\"font-size: 16px\">retrieve_password()</code></li><li>Les en-t√™tes de th√®mes prennent maintenant en charge les instructions  ‚ÄúRequires at least‚Äù et ‚ÄúRequires PHP‚Äù</li><li>La capacit√©¬†<code style=\"font-size: 16px\">delete_posts</code>¬†ne d√©clenchera plus d&rsquo;avertissements PHP pour les types de publications personnalis√©s</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Tout est d√©taill√© en anglais sur cette note de d√©veloppement&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"GTxbJT1rBG\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/02/26/miscellaneous-developer-focused-changes-in-wordpress-5-4/\">Miscellaneous Developer Focused Changes in WordPress 5.4</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Miscellaneous Developer Focused Changes in WordPress 5.4&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/02/26/miscellaneous-developer-focused-changes-in-wordpress-5-4/embed/#?secret=GTxbJT1rBG\" data-secret=\"GTxbJT1rBG\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<p>Pour rappel, la sortie de WordPress 5.4 est pr√©vue le 31 mars 2020. Vous pouvez d‚Äôores et d√©j√† la tester en version¬†<em>Release Candidate</em>¬†en installant l‚Äôextension officielle WordPress Beta Tester puis en allant dans ses r√©glages et en cochant la case¬†<em>¬´¬†Beta¬†¬ª</em>¬†/ version de d√©veloppement puis en mettant √† jour votre installation de fa√ßon classique.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"iswXokV2Ox\"><a href=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/\">WordPress Beta Tester</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"¬´¬†WordPress Beta Tester¬†¬ª &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/embed/#?secret=iswXokV2Ox\" data-secret=\"iswXokV2Ox\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/03/04/les-changements-techniques-a-venir-dans-wordpress-5-4/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\